OL,3,CMore checks could 'possibly' have
OL,4,Csaved teenager's life - NHS trust
OL,6,FAn NHS trust has admitted that more
OL,7,Ffrequent monitoring of a vulnerable
OL,8,Fteenager may have prevented her death.
OL,10,FCariss Stone died aged 19 in August
OL,11,F2019, two days after being found with
OL,12,Fa ligature around her neck at a
OL,13,Fpsychiatric intensive care unit.
OL,15,F, Somerset NHS Foundation Trust said
OL,16,Fthe teenager, who was from, could
OL,17,F"possibly" have been saved if she had
OL,18,Fbeen more frequently monitored.
