OL,3,CMore checks could 'possibly' have
OL,4,Csaved teenager's life - NHS trust
OL,6,FThe former Strode College student had
OL,7,Fa history of self-harm and at the time
OL,8,Fof her death was judged a high enough
OL,9,Frisk to herself to need welfare checks
OL,10,Fseveral times an hour.
OL,12,FDr Lucy Knight, Medical Director of
OL,13,FSomerset NHS Foundation Trust, told
OL,14,Fthe jury at Wells Town Hall that there
OL,15,Fwas confusion among staff as to how
OL,16,Foften Cariss needed monitored.
