OL,3,CMore checks could 'possibly' have
OL,4,Csaved teenager's life - NHS trust
OL,6,FShe had been judged to require NHS
OL,7,Fstandard Level 2 observation - which
OL,8,Fincludes welfare checks five times an
OL,9,Fhour - at random intervals - and not
OL,10,Fmore than 15 minutes apart.
OL,12,FThe jury heard that a nurse in charge
OL,13,Fof Holford Ward, the facility in
OL,14,FTaunton where Cariss was detained, had
OL,15,Fdecided to implement patient checks
OL,16,Fevery five minutes and had given staff
OL,17,Frecord sheets with pre-printed five-
OL,18,Fminute check times.
