OL,3,CMore checks could 'possibly' have
OL,4,Csaved teenager's life - NHS trust
OL,6,FShe added that she believed a five-
OL,7,Fminute regime was unrealistic and
OL,8,Fcould cause extra stress to
OL,9,Fpsychiatric patients.
OL,11,FThe inquest previously heard how
OL,12,FCariss had struggled with anorexia and
OL,13,Fself harm since she was 14, and the
OL,14,Fsummer before she died she had been
OL,15,Ffound using a ligature on 55 occasions.
OL,17,FThe jury has heard from 30 witnesses
OL,18,Fand is due to start deliberations
OL,19,Ftomorrow.
